column1: Project title: ONION MAGGOT/SHAPE X SIZE TRIAL "SIZE" JUNE 2006

column2: Evaluate onion maggot fly attraction to  traps of different size
Different size spherical traps were covered with sticky material and placed in the field in 2006.  Male and Female onion maggot stuck to the traps were evaluated

column1: Original document and project brief received from Brian Nault in late 2018, data entered into tabular form in this document May 7, 2019
